text: El Dorado is a neighborhood in northeast Houston, Texas, United States. The site of a halfway house, El Dorado had the highest amount of convicted felons per resident of all of the Houston neighborhoods in 2007.Fehling, Dave. "The ex-cons next door ." KHOU-TV.
